307
00:27:29,345 --> 00:27:34,568
So for that blood pressure check, if they've got a blood pressure cuff at home, we can call them, we can talk to them.

308
00:27:35,109 --> 00:27:38,231
Even things like rash, we're getting everyone trained up to do video visits.

309
00:27:38,684 --> 00:27:43,745
so that you can see someone in their home and not necessarily bring them into the clinic where they might be exposed.

310
00:27:44,266 --> 00:27:46,326
So we're completely transforming how we do care.

311
00:27:46,906 --> 00:27:56,869
